patient</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining to dropsy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dropsicalness</ent>⟦br⟧
